{"tid":2055907,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論35+合併名單可行性] 立法會地區直選既制度叫做「黑爾數額名單比例代表制」","createTime":"2020-06-08T10:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T13:20:37.000Z","uid":5523,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0df499d95850d6f2d1081dda2faa9cb370278e99","tid":2055907,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"乜撚野名單呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去片!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p59mZyffEao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp59mZyffEao&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=98dce741\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p59mZyffEao</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr97-98/chinese/sec/library/cin1_plc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr97-98%2Fchinese%2Fsec%2Flibrary%2Fcin1_plc.pdf&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=c4c81795\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr97-98/chinese/sec/library/cin1_plc.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n以下討論泛民本土聯營既聯合名單可行性<br />\n假設黃陣營以初選得出聯合名單既排名<br />\n每個地區選區只用1張名單出選<br />\n達到完全集中選票<br />\n以下係本小學雞加減數excel試計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuz5tLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwuz5tLy.png&h=e301bb55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n假設藍方全知全能, 用配票方法達到最大得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而黃方集中票原以一張名單出選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以見到黃藍比例岩岩好6:4時, 雙方無人有得益<br />\n黃藍比例係59:41時黃方會有1%得益<br />\n而藍方必然有損失<br />\n而黃藍比例係58:42時<br />\n如果藍方配票得宜可以得到8%既得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而從excel睇到, 假如只有2方對決而無第3方既情況下,<br />\n浪費既選票將會係0和遊戲<br />\n有人得益就必然有人有損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 數學唔合格, 有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11259024d13d4c5f2739a7e846cf077a96e0be46","tid":2055907,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"討論pls"},{"pid":"361746c8451883170e390ce6fdaa206042aa46f0","tid":2055907,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T11:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919a7577a0d161a1be685c222660b1776d7383d1","tid":2055907,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11259024d13d4c5f2739a7e846cf077a96e0be46","tid":2055907,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"討論pls"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95757fefd764b7baf0e688c397fd1a8026cd2b3","tid":2055907,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b60a3b08890123a40f7330f19e4d10f81c61d3","tid":2055907,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1545243ca992aa601bc69485a6a567d66ff49d86","tid":2055907,"uid":344249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"我覺得只會重現2004年新東鑽石名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02829e5984cec2b6cd25f24cb4a5eaa8607f815","tid":2055907,"uid":17506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuz5tLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwuz5tLy.png&h=e301bb55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用返你個表一,6:4得票果個做例子<br />\n假設2陣營都能夠平均分配得票+想爭多d議席:黃營600/7=85.7,藍營400/5=80<br />\n理論上黃:藍議席上係做到7:3<br />\n所以點計都係靠配票方式黎爭最多議席,只係風險會大左d<br />\n<br />\n但事實上泛民之前係配票都有過成功既例子,只係近幾屆內鬥不斷先至冇咁成功<br />\n<br />\n分區配票的始祖要算是民主黨。話說2000年立法會選舉，民主黨為了想奪得新界西3個議席，因此亦分拆3張名單參選，分別由李永達、何俊仁及陳偉業3人領軍。為了使選票較平均地分佈在3張名單上，以同時提高3張名單的勝算，民主黨採用了劃分「選票責任區」的方法，把葵青及離島分配給李永達；屯門及元朗鄉郊分配給何俊仁；至於荃灣、元朗市中心和天水圍，及1.5個屯門區議會的選區，則分配給陳偉業。每位候選人負責集中火力在自己所屬的責任區內拉票。雖然街板及海報仍舊可以在整個新界西懸掛及張貼，但3人只可以在所屬責任區內企街、洗樓、派單張，及寄上選舉郵遞廣告，不可以未經批准而跨區宣傳。結果，李永達、何俊仁及陳偉業3人，分別在自己負責的葵青、屯門及荃灣，取得該黨近七成半、八成半，以及九成之選票，民主黨的配票策略可說是十分成功。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/20160920/s00022/1474337524015/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E3%80%91%E5%88%86%E5%8D%80%E9%85%8D%E7%A5%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%88%90%E6%95%88%EF%BC%88%E6%96%87-%E8%94%A1%E5%AD%90%E5%BC%B7-%E9%99%B3%E9%9B%8B%E6%96%87%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20160920%2Fs00022%2F1474337524015%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2585%258D%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2595%2588%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E9%259B%258B%25E6%2596%2587%25EF%25BC%2589&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KYMLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=4fa33737\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20160920%2Fs00022%2F1474337524015%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2585%258D%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2595%2588%25EF%25BC%2588%25E6%2596%2587-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E9%259B%258B%25E6%2596%2587%25EF%25BC%2589&h=e7a7d710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/article/2